cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.DS, cs.LG, cs.NA 

This paper deals with image segmentation and inpainting, which are primarily computer vision and graphics tasks, hence cs.CV and cs.GR are the most likely categories. The paper also involves optimization and linear programming, which fall under cs.DS and cs.NA. Finally, the paper discusses the formulation of the problem and the use of constraints, which are topics covered in cs.LG.
